  }, "v2"), mdx("p", null, "\u0110\xE2y l\xE0 l\u1EDDi CH\xDAA To\xE0n N\u0103ng ph\xE1n: 'Khi \xCDt-ra-en ra kh\u1ECFi Ai-c\u1EADp, qu\xE2n A-ma-l\xE9c t\xECm c\xE1ch ng\u0103n kh\xF4ng cho h\u1ECD v\xE0o Ca-na-an. Cho n\xEAn ta s\u1EBD tr\u1EEBng ph\u1EA1t ch\xFAng. "), mdx("h6", {
