  }, "v18"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\xE0i sai ng\u01B0\u01A1i thi h\xE0nh m\u1ED9t s\u1EE9 m\u1EA1ng. Ng\xE0i b\u1EA3o, 'H\xE3y \u0111i di\u1EC7t h\u1EBFt d\xE2n gian \xE1c \u0111\xF3, l\xE0 d\xE2n A-ma-l\xE9c. H\xE3y g\xE2y chi\u1EBFn v\u1EDBi ch\xFAng n\xF3 cho \u0111\u1EBFn khi tuy\u1EC7t di\u1EC7t ch\xFAng n\xF3.' "), mdx("h6", {
