  }, "v30"), mdx("p", null, "Sau-l\u01A1 \u0111\xE1p, \"T\xF4i \u0111\xE3 ph\u1EA1m t\u1ED9i. Nh\u01B0ng xin \xF4ng h\xE3y t\xF4n tr\u1ECDng t\xF4i tr\u01B0\u1EDBc m\u1EB7t c\xE1c b\xF4 l\xE3o c\u1EE7a d\xE2n t\xF4i v\xE0 tr\u01B0\u1EDBc m\u1EB7t c\u1EA3 d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en. H\xE3y tr\u1EDF l\u1EA1i c\xF9ng t\xF4i \u0111\u1EC3 t\xF4i c\xF3 th\u1EC3 th\u1EDD l\u1EA1y CH\xDAA l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF \xF4ng.\" "), mdx("h6", {
